# Nano Banana (Gemini) API Configuration
#
# The API key can now be configured in two ways:
# 1. Through the Settings modal in the application UI
# 2. Through environment variables (for development/deployment)
#
# For local development, you can optionally set:
# VITE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
#
# However, the recommended approach is to use the Settings modal in the app.
# The API key will be stored securely in your browser's localStorage.

# Optional: For development/build time API key (not recommended for production)
# VITE_API_KEY=AIza_...
